  <summary date="2020-12-31T17:28:58Z" status="Introduced in House">PPE for Safe Schools Act

This bill provides funding for grants to state educational agencies and, through them, subgrants to local educational agencies to purchase sanitation supplies and personal protective equipment, provide staff training, and hire additional support staff to clean and sanitize school facilities and buses.</summary>
